acter_id";s:1:"3";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Dusk_Glow";s:4:"text";s:61:"Her backstory is super deep. Really one of my very best works";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424154510";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fb8bf8";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14241545077";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d5a9ff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1262519;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1262519";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11835";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Dusk_Glow";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1276";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Milagra_Lilac";s:4:"text";s:295:"I&#039;ve only ever had three OCs. One of which I gave away because I had no idea how to play him. He was definitely the best looking one. He could fit right into the show. My other OCs, Able Ace, known as Able now, simply. And Dusk Glow...well, it took me an hour to think of their names alone.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424154598";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#049010";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14241545954";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0a991d";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1262523;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1262523";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11835";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Dusk_Glow";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1276";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Milagra_Lilac";s:4:"text";s:101:"That&#039;s an hour each, mind you. I had Able for about a year before I even attempted a second OC. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424154655";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#049010";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14241546418";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0a991d";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1262528;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1262528";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Milagra_Lilac";s:12:"character_id";s:1:"3";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Dusk_Glow";s:4:"text";s:51:"Well, I&#039;d love to help you brainstorm sometime";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424154735";s:15:"chat_name_